---
💡 Final Summary
INNER JOIN → Only matching
LEFT JOIN → All left + matching right
RIGHT JOIN → All right + matching left
FULL JOIN → Everything
---
🚀 Pro Tip (Very Important)
👉 Always use aliases:
students s, courses c
👉 Makes query clean & professional
